Cell["\<\
As we are dealing with symmetric spinors, it is not so important to display \
the indices of the spinors. Hence, it makes sense to work with the spinors \
without giving indices to them. Therefore the display form of the tensors are \
changed so that it is displayed according to PrintAs even if no indices are \
given.\
\>", "MathCaption",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8399293065961523`*^9, 
  3.839929482074967*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"19e75f74-31a3-45e7-9449-\
