Cell["\<\
Observe that for equations with TensorPlus, one should use ZeroTensor instead \
of 0 because it retains the valence information.\[LineSeparator]One can \
easily construct a ZeroTensor object with the same valence numbers as any \
given tensor with ZeroTensorOfTensor.\
\>", "MathCaption",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8399300261487365`*^9, 
