Cell["\<\
Due to the symmetry, we can work with the SymMult objects without indices. \
They can also be sorted with respect to a given sorting function. The default \
sorting is mainly according to total valence.\[LineSeparator]\
\>", "MathCaption",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.839931447963462*^9, 3.839931484298389*^9}, {
