Cell["\<\
At this point we do not have a way to canonicalize expressions with respect \
to these commutation rules.\
\>", "MathCaption",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.839932932213467*^9, 
  3.8399330100219793`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a34e21a3-b9b4-4758-af79-\
8b3c45499444"],

Cell["\<\
If we do irreducible decompositions of all spinors, and split the equations \
into irreducible parts, we can form any algebraic spinor equation with \
SymMult, MultScal, TensorPlus and ZeroTensor. Covariant derivatives can be \
handled with fundamental spinor operators.\
\>", "MathCaption",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8399314175001593`*^9, 3.839931424572254*^9}, {
  3.8399324578530617`*^9, 
  3.8399326380674477`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"db191145-9a3a-4187-aec1-\
e74cea1aaf7b"]
}, Closed]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Fundamental spinor operators", "SubsubsectionIcon",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.518749770615905*^9, 3.518749781317524*^9}, {
   3.5441000811725874`*^9, 3.54410009418301*^9}, 3.5449509679572973`*^9, {
   3.545113058582131*^9, 3.5451130709997525`*^9}, 3.545113835182695*^9, {
   3.5681238965127745`*^9, 3.568123898384777*^9}, {3.592121533378827*^9, 
   3.5921215409888377`*^9}, {3.592133328760397*^9, 3.592133330470399*^9}, 
   3.8400041798573627`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"ea64ae12-118a-405f-9be6-\
15d5675ce629"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Any covariant spinor derivative acting on a symmetric spinor can be split \
into at most 4 different irreducible parts. We call these irreducible parts \
of the derivative ",
 StyleBox["fundamental spinor operators",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ". The fundamental spinor operators corresponding to a spinor covariant \
derivative is defined by the function DefFundSpinOperators. This also defines \
a set of tools to handle them. All names that are defined will end with the \
name of the covariant derivative. This way it is possible to handle \
fundamental spinor operators for several covariant derivatives at the same \
time."
}], "MathCaption",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.518749805372766*^9, 3.518749875448089*^9}, {
   3.5441001053214297`*^9, 3.544100145725501*^9}, 3.5449509679728975`*^9, 
   3.545113835182695*^9, {3.59212073596671*^9, 3.592120744176722*^9}, {
   3.5921215560888586`*^9, 3.592121605748928*^9}, {3.592121900489341*^9, 
   3.5921219403293962`*^9}, {3.5921219716094403`*^9, 3.592122262309847*^9}, {
   3.592122301449902*^9, 3.592122337759953*^9}, {3.5921223932100306`*^9, 
   3.592122420520069*^9}, {3.5921224508301115`*^9, 3.592122483700157*^9}, 
   3.5995505697608275`*^9, 
   3.838805927129534*^9},ExpressionUUID->"9433c995-fbd3-42c8-8b35-\
68161f91880b"],

